tical response functions computed in local thermodynamic\nequilibrium (through SIR), modified with fixed departure coefficients to\nincorporate NLTE effects in chromospheric spectral lines. This publication\ndescribes the operating fundamentals of DeSIRe and describes its behaviour,\nrobustness, stability, and speed. The code is ready to be used by the solar\ncommunity and is being made publicly available.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 4 Feb 2022 16:51:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-20"}
