ate accurate, personalized encoding models and, subsequently, personalized\noptimal synthetic images for new individuals scanned under different\nexperimental conditions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 4 Feb 2022 17:24:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 15 May 2022 02:52:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-17"}
