 highly efficient. Among 27 shortest attack traces revealed by\nthe attack graphs, 62.8% are not anticipated by the system administrator. It\nonly takes 1.2 seconds to generate and analyze the attack graph for an IoT\nsystem consisting of 50 devices.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 5 Feb 2022 07:33:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-08"}
